info.author: Sylvain Thenault
info.description:
Pyreverse is a set of utilities to reverse enginering Python
code. It uses a representation of a Python project in a class hierarchy which
can be used to extract any information (such as generating UML diagrams or 
unit tests, as pyargo and py2tests)

Pyreverse has now been integrated to pylint : http://pypi.python.org/pypi/pylint/
